{
  "intro": [
    "Principal Commentators",
    "Commentators most frequently consulted, will be thus marked --- B. Bristow, C. Calmet, Ch. Challoner, D. Du Hamel, E. Estius, J. Jansenius, M. Menochius, P. Pastorini or Walmesey, Po. Polus, T. Tirinus, V. Bible de Vence, W. Worthington, Wi. Witham. The Rev. Fr. Haydock's original observations, or such, at least, as he could not easily trace to their real authors, either through forgetfulness, or because he adopted some alteration, or received them from some of his learned friends, whose names he was not at liberty to mention will be marked in the Old Testament with the letter H, while additional notes in the New Testament will be marked with the letter A. The names of other authors, who may be occasionally consulted, will be given at length.",
